name: Cherry AI
description: Cherry AI is a Telegram-native platform that powers a suite of tools for Web3 communities, offering multichain functionality and AI-driven features. Its flagship product, Cherry Bot, is installed in over 200K Telegram groups and actively used by more than 110K Web3 communities, serving a user base of over 12 million. The platform has generated $5 million in on-chain revenue since late 2024, positioning it as a revenue-backed infrastructure layer in the Web3 space.
